pc|dq|at|If East plays second hand low (the play that worked when a low diamond was led), |
pg| ***** 142 ***** |


pc|d4|at|West will win the @DK. |
pg| ***** 143 ***** |


pc|ddk|
pg| ***** 144 ***** |


wt|n|at|^^^^When declarer eventually leads a second round of diamonds from the dummy, |
