pc|d2|at|the @DJ will be certain to win a trick either now or later (depending on whether East plays his @DA or not). |
pg| ***** 146 ***** |


up|4|

nt|^b@2^z@3So if East plays second hand low on the lead of the @DQ, South will win a diamond trick. |
