at|If instead East chooses to cover an honor with an honor by playing his @DA, |
pg| ***** 148 ***** |


pc|dadd|
pg| ***** 149 ***** |


at|the declarer will not win a diamond trick since West still has the @DK109 over declarer's @DJ8. |
pg| ***** 150 ***** |


up|3|at|^^^^Second hand low and cover an honor with an honor cannot both be right at the same time. |
