at|In this particular situation, cover an honor with an honor is the winner!|
pg| ***** 152 ***** |


up|1|wt|s|

nt|^b@2^z@3If South starts diamonds by leading the @DJ out of his hand, |
pg| ***** 153 ***** |


pc|dj|at|the result is the same. If West plays second hand low (as he should when South leads a low diamond instead of the @DJ), |
